content.text:
We're Brogan, Nick, and Zack  three lifelong friends with a passion for hot sauce. The first time we whipped up a test batch of Happy Boy, we knew we had cracked the condiment code. We'd never tasted a pepper sauce that was so packed with flavor  our original hot sauce recipe had to be shared with the world!

Fast forward to today, and we're doing just that. Our production facility in Scranton, PA may be small, but that's the way we like it for achieving small batches with BIG flavor.

Happy Boy now comes in 3 flavors to add to your hot sauce collection, and we recently launched our premium jerky line, which we call Sauced-Up Jerky. We hope you'll join us on this journey of creating high-quality hot sauces, handcrafted jerky, and more!
Brogan recently interviewed on the podcast *Gettin' to Know the 570!* You can find the episode titled...

'*Gettin' to Know Brogan Scotch:
Co-Owner of Scotch Sauce
Based out of Scranton*'
